WEBVTT

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:32.200
kilomita 30 kusini mwa mji
wa Ifakara kupitia mto.

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:37.136
Kila jioni tulienda kwenye vijiji
na tochi na mabomba.

00:01:37.160 --> 00:01:38.720
Tulikunja suruali zetu,

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:42.696
na kungojea mbu ambao
walikuja kutung'ata

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:44.296
ili tuweze kuwakusanya

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:46.178
kuwaangalia kama wamebeba malaria.

00:01:46.202 --> 00:01:47.216
(Kicheko)

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:49.416
Mimi na mwenzangu
tulichagua kaya,

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:53.280
na tukaanza ndani na nje,
tukibadilishana nafasi kila nusu saa.

00:01:54.440 --> 00:01:58.200
Na tulifanya hivi kwa masaa 12 kila usiku
kwa usiku 24 mfululizo.

00:01:59.160 --> 00:02:01.576
Tulilala kwa masaa manne kila asubuhi